  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Fleet and corporate customers wash now and pay later.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.437,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "This is where they live.",
      "startS": 3.786,
      "endS": 5.082,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Portfolio totals up top, three insight panels, and the account list below.",
      "startS": 5.755,
      "endS": 7.425,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "When a fleet manager calls about a bill, you start on this screen.",
      "startS": 7.813,
      "endS": 14.957,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Four numbers, the whole book.",
      "startS": 15.36,
      "endS": 17.294,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "How many accounts you carry, how many are live, what they owe you right now,",
      "startS": 17.982,
      "endS": 20.583,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "and the average credit line you extend.",
      "startS": 20.825,
      "endS": 24.338,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Outstanding is the one your callers care about.",
      "startS": 25.118,
      "endS": 27.462,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "It is the money on the street.",
      "startS": 27.737,
      "endS": 29.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Three panels read the portfolio's health.",
      "startS": 29.676,
      "endS": 31.755,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "A balance trend over the year, credit use broken out by location,",
      "startS": 32.388,
      "endS": 34.051,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "and the split of active, suspended, and closed.",
      "startS": 34.38,
      "endS": 36.38,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Watch the utilization bars.",
      "startS": 36.677,
      "endS": 39.584,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "An account near its limit is an account about to decline.",
      "startS": 40.346,
      "endS": 45.2,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Down to the list card.",
      "startS": 45.6,
      "endS": 48.29,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Three buttons sit here.",
      "startS": 48.29,
      "endS": 49.979,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "One of them, Generate Invoices, runs month-end billing across every account",
      "startS": 49.979,
      "endS": 53.641,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "and sends real invoices.",
      "startS": 53.641,
      "endS": 54.973,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "We locate it and we leave it alone.",
      "startS": 54.973,
      "endS": 58.146,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Know where it lives; never press it on a whim.",
      "startS": 58.146,
      "endS": 61.996,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "The rest is a familiar list.",
      "startS": 62.473,
      "endS": 64.081,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Search by account, company, or contact.",
      "startS": 64.568,
      "endS": 66.984,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Filters beside it.",
      "startS": 67.463,
      "endS": 68.426,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Seven columns, ending in status.",
      "startS": 68.829,
      "endS": 70.879,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "If you have worked the Customer List, you already know this one.",
      "startS": 71.554,
      "endS": 74.696,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Open one account.",
      "startS": 75.181,
      "endS": 76.05,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Click a row and the full account view opens.",
      "startS": 76.05,
      "endS": 79.256,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "In the demo tenant every row opens the same sample account,",
      "startS": 79.256,
      "endS": 82.741,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "so read the numbers as a layout, not as one real customer.",
      "startS": 82.741,
      "endS": 86.219,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "The shape is what matters.",
      "startS": 86.219,
      "endS": 87.902,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "The header is the account at a glance.",
      "startS": 88.32,
      "endS": 91.139,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Company name, an active badge,",
      "startS": 91.139,
      "endS": 92.673,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "then the account number, home location, and primary contact on one line.",
      "startS": 92.673,
      "endS": 96.353,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Three chips carry the terms:",
      "startS": 96.353,
      "endS": 98.667,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "net thirty, a ten thousand dollar limit, fourteen vehicles.",
      "startS": 98.667,
      "endS": 101.679,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "You know the deal before you read a single tab.",
      "startS": 101.679,
      "endS": 105.164,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Five buttons up top.",
      "startS": 105.6,
      "endS": 106.984,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Back and search are safe.",
      "startS": 107.605,
      "endS": 109.201,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Statement, delete, and edit change or generate records,",
      "startS": 109.868,
      "endS": 113.343,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "so on a support call you read them and stop.",
      "startS": 113.611,
      "endS": 116.22,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Nothing here gets clicked today.",
      "startS": 116.719,
      "endS": 118.453,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Six metrics run under the header.",
      "startS": 118.88,
      "endS": 120.678,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Total balance, available credit, the limit, a monthly average,",
      "startS": 121.155,
      "endS": 123.133,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "the last payment date, and when the account opened.",
      "startS": 123.448,
      "endS": 124.03,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Balance and available credit add up to the limit,",
      "startS": 124.46,
      "endS": 128.586,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "so one look tells you how much room is left.",
      "startS": 129.29,
      "endS": 134.046,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Beside the band, a set of quick counts.",
      "startS": 134.544,
      "endS": 137.032,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Vehicles, invoices, payments, documents.",
      "startS": 138.046,
      "endS": 141.248,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "They are shortcuts into the same records the tabs hold,",
      "startS": 141.681,
      "endS": 144.521,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "with the totals right on the chip.",
      "startS": 144.751,
      "endS": 146.544,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Ten tabs across the account.",
      "startS": 147.059,
      "endS": 148.74,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Overview, details, contacts, vehicles, invoices, payments,",
      "startS": 149.306,
      "endS": 149.952,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "activity, documents, notes, and audit trail.",
      "startS": 150.244,
      "endS": 150.978,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "You will not touch all ten on a call.",
      "startS": 151.245,
      "endS": 151.983,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Knowing they exist means you never have to guess where a fact is stored.",
      "startS": 152.243,
      "endS": 165.048,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Overview opens on the billing story.",
      "startS": 165.52,
      "endS": 167.526,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Monthly charges show the average month, the peak month, and last month, over the past year.",
      "startS": 167.832,
      "endS": 172.841,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "This is the account's normal rhythm.",
      "startS": 173.127,
      "endS": 174.911,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "It is what you compare against when a charge looks wrong.",
      "startS": 175.115,
      "endS": 177.665,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Now the panel that earns this lesson.",
      "startS": 178.295,
      "endS": 180.327,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Aging splits what the account owes by how long it has gone unpaid:",
      "startS": 180.841,
      "endS": 184.814,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "current, thirty to sixty, sixty to ninety, ninety plus, and a total.",
      "startS": 185.14,
      "endS": 189.241,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "Older buckets are older debt.",
      "startS": 189.589,
      "endS": 190.382,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "Anything sitting in ninety plus is the account most likely to get suspended.",
      "startS": 190.951,
      "endS": 192.641,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "Read this before you promise a customer anything.",
      "startS": 192.986,
      "endS": 200.078,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "Two more panels finish the picture.",
      "startS": 200.48,
      "endS": 203.262,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "Wash frequency shows how hard the fleet is using its vehicles.",
      "startS": 203.262,
      "endS": 206.824,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Account health rolls up credit use, a payment score, and average days to pay.",
      "startS": 206.824,
      "endS": 212.025,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "Payment score and days to pay are your fast read",
      "startS": 212.025,
      "endS": 216.199,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "on whether this account pays like clockwork or drags its feet.",
      "startS": 216.199,
      "endS": 219.76,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "Click into invoices.",
      "startS": 220.248,
      "endS": 221.193,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "Every bill the account has been sent, with its amount, what has been paid,",
      "startS": 221.193,
      "endS": 225.983,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "the balance, and a status of paid, open, or overdue.",
      "startS": 225.983,
      "endS": 229.134,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "When someone asks about a specific charge,",
      "startS": 229.134,
      "endS": 231.949,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s15",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "this is where you find the invoice behind it.",
      "startS": 231.949,
      "endS": 234.785,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p76",
      "text": "Then payments.",
      "startS": 235.269,
      "endS": 235.923,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p77",
      "text": "The ledger shows each payment, how it was applied to invoices,",
      "startS": 235.923,
      "endS": 240.163,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p78",
      "text": "the method, and who posted it.",
      "startS": 240.163,
      "endS": 242.126,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p79",
      "text": "Watch the status column.",
      "startS": 242.126,
      "endS": 244.243,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p80",
      "text": "A voided row explains a payment that looked received but was reversed,",
      "startS": 244.243,
      "endS": 248.624,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s16",
      "id": "p81",
      "text": "which is often the real answer to a billing dispute.",
      "startS": 248.624,
      "endS": 252.24,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p82",
      "text": "The rest of the tabs, in a sentence each.",
      "startS": 252.64,
      "endS": 254.966,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p83",
      "text": "Details is the full record.",
      "startS": 256.267,
      "endS": 258.037,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p84",
      "text": "Contacts, the people.",
      "startS": 259.029,
      "endS": 260.469,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p85",
      "text": "Vehicles, the fleet roster.",
      "startS": 261.678,
      "endS": 263.532,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p86",
      "text": "Documents holds agreements.",
      "startS": 264.57,
      "endS": 266.384,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p87",
      "text": "Notes carries internal comments, some for everyone and some for management only.",
      "startS": 267.615,
      "endS": 272.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p88",
      "text": "Audit trail is the change history.",
      "startS": 273.58,
      "endS": 275.565,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s17",
      "id": "p89",
      "text": "Activity would be the live feed, but it did not load at capture, so we park it.",
      "startS": 276.608,
      "endS": 281.011,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p90",
      "text": "Back to the list.",
      "startS": 281.501,
      "endS": 282.422,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p91",
      "text": "That is a house account, end to end.",
      "startS": 282.883,
      "endS": 284.238,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p92",
      "text": "The list gives you the portfolio and the billing button you never run casually.",
      "startS": 284.486,
      "endS": 285.304,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p93",
      "text": "The detail gives you one account's balance, its aging,",
      "startS": 285.791,
      "endS": 290.364,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p94",
      "text": "and the invoices and payments that answer where a charge came from.",
      "startS": 290.832,
      "endS": 297.451,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s18",
      "id": "p95",
      "text": "Next time a fleet manager calls, you know the path.",
      "startS": 297.826,
      "endS": 300.559,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}